cast.overview: Following the events of Captain America: Civil War, Peter Parker, with the help of his mentor Tony Stark, tries to balance his life as an ordinary high school student in Queens, New York City, with fighting crime as his superhero alter ego Spider-Man as a new threat, the Vulture, emerges.
cast.title: Spider-Man: Homecoming

details.biography: Cassidy Kahler is an American Actress and Stunt Performer from Sonoma, California. Cassidy began her career as a competitive gymnast and dancer. In her early teens she entered the theatre and began acting consistently. Cassidy continued her passion of the arts through high school and college. She later transitioned into film professionally.
details.name: Cassidy Alexandra Kahler
